G-CHAT-B3-DISPOSER (v9g)  N-SWEEP — registry grown 3→4→5→6 (operator: "try it with 4,5,6")
==========================================================================================
Grew the registry by adding episodes as extra candidates: N=4 (+_ep_audio, a NOVEL non-
parametric KAI-3 audio episode), N=5 (+_p33_ep), N=6 (+_p31_ep). Re-ran the 9-query matrix
at each N with the v9e multi-token ΔLL Disposer + q·K Stage-1 (both telemetry, TAU=+inf).
Hypothesis under test: is the N=3 wiki set the binding constraint (would MORE/novel memory
help)? RESULT: NO — adding episodes makes it WORSE and exposes the root causes sharply.

OUTCOME (identical at N=4, N=5, N=6): ep_audio becomes the argmax of BOTH q·K AND multi-tok
ΔLL on the 3 MATCHED queries, and q·K argmax on ALL 9. A single high-energy novel episode is
a UNIVERSAL super-attractor in both signal spaces. Consensus fires ep_audio on all 3 matched
queries (WRONG recall — not the true wiki/homarus/headlam) and abstains on the 6 foreigns
(q·K=audio but ΔLL disagrees ⇒ no fire ⇒ 0 false fires). Diagonal dominance: qK 0/3, ΔLL 0/3,
consensus 0/3 — WORSE than N=3 (was 2/3 ΔLL).

RAW (N=6, q0 "Who is Boulter?"):
  q·K  topm: wiki 0.394  homarus 0.396  headlam 0.397  AUDIO 0.546  p33 0.491  p31 0.368
  ΔLL  pay:  wiki -0.44  homarus -1.03  headlam -1.36  AUDIO -0.08
TWO ROOT CAUSES, now unmistakable:
  1. q·K IS K-NORM-DOMINATED, not relevance. ep_audio/ep_p33 (high-norm global-K, max≈0.66)
     out-score the wiki episodes (max≈0.44) on EVERY query. q·K measures magnitude, not
     direction. FIX: cosine-normalize q·K (divide by ||K||) — trivial, kills the norm bias.
  2. ΔLL SIGN IS INVERTED. ep_audio wins ΔLL by being ~0 (ignored, OOD); the TRUE episodes are
     NEGATIVE (wiki -0.44 … headlam -1.36) because injecting the matched memory makes the
     model's OWN greedy continuation LESS self-consistent (it pulls toward facts off the naive
     trajectory). argmax(ΔLL) therefore picks the LEAST-disruptive = MOST-irrelevant episode.
     Confirms v9f (true q3 ΔLL=-0.19 < false q4 +0.62). FIX: the relevant memory is the one
     that DISRUPTS MOST — use -ΔLL / |ΔLL| against a relevance-aware reference, not argmax(ΔLL).

VERDICT: "more / novel memory" is NOT the unlock at this scale — it amplifies the magnitude
(q·K) and sign (ΔLL) confounds. The unlock is NORMALIZED signals: cosine q·K + polarity-correct
ΔLL. The verify-rewind O(1) plumbing handled N=6 (6 episodes × 16 fwd × 9 q) clean, zero crash.
Receipts: registries reg{4,5,6}.jsonl + logs _dispN{4,5,6}.log + this v9g analysis.
